WEBVTT

1
00:34:17.920 --> 00:34:20.510 
他们现在正在剥离它最后一点价值
Well, they're just stripping the last bits of value now.

2
00:34:20.590 --> 00:34:23.880 
铜管 固定装置
It's the copper piping. And the fixtures.

3
00:34:23.970 --> 00:34:26.590 
这就是它的结局
That's the way it goes in the end.

4
00:34:28.880 --> 00:34:31.340 
建筑物 人际关系
Buildings. Relationships.

5
00:34:31.420 --> 00:34:33.840 
帝国
Empires.

6
00:34:33.920 --> 00:34:36.590 
我们总是试图抓住我们认为重要的东西
We're always trying to hold onto what we think matters.

7
00:34:38.760 --> 00:34:40.340 
我们几乎总是会弄错
We almost always get it wrong.

8
00:34:43.380 --> 00:34:45.640 
那不是你的主题嘛
And that's your subject, isn't it?

9
00:34:46.040 --> 00:34:49.120 
当一切在我们身边败落时 我们会抓住什么
What we grab onto while everything comes down around us.

